<plot>Delhi-based Neha, the only child of widower Major Balwant Singh, gets a message to visit an ailing Colonel Mahendra Kapoor, who lives in Manali, Himachal Pradesh. On her way by bus, she reflects on her life and the changes that have taken place over the last six months, not knowing that even more life altering changes await her after she reaches her destination.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?658979</url></doc>
